<p><tt><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-1763-ex">SCP-1763</a> is a semi-metaphysical entity capable of excising itself at will from various aspects of reality, both real and imagined. SCP-1763 is currently both invisible and silent, possesses no heat-signature, can render itself selectively intangible, and is capable of exerting a strong memetic effect on nearby humans&#8230;</strong></tt></p>
